--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 0}
  m_Name: Dialogue3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - speakerName: Iroha
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 681f82db4902e9a4fa3fe39f7f30c840, type: 3}
    content: Well... here you go. I hope they're at least edible, Kaguya
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ca85ad29208a0e346b547ca4d8a6e937, type: 3}
    content: (Takes a thoughtful bite) Hmm... they're not quite fluffy, and a little
      dense.
  - speakerName: Iroha
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 681f82db4902e9a4fa3fe39f7f30c840, type: 3}
    content: (Disappointed) I see...
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ca85ad29208a0e346b547ca4d8a6e937, type: 3}
    content: But, (Takes another bite) they have a very honest, handmade taste. They
      taste like you.
  - speakerName: Iroha
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 681f82db4902e9a4fa3fe39f7f30c840, type: 3}
    content: Like me...?
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ca85ad29208a0e346b547ca4d8a6e937, type: 3}
    content: Yes. A little clumsy, but full of warmth. Thank you, Iroha. I'll finish
      them all.
